body: This is more accessible, semantically correct, and better for SEO. See: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements#Usage_notes ~~We should also in the future make sure that .md documents with a title specified in the front-matter start their headings at `##`.~~ After discussion on IRC, we will now automatically increment headings by 1 instead of requiring the contributor to fix their markdown. --- This change is [](https://reviewable.io/reviews/toktok/website/26)
